The meaning of a word is the use of the word
[Wittgenstein]
[哲学探究]
	1-6
		>But what does the word "five" mean? --The question here was not about the meaning of the word "five" at all. The only question was how the word "five" was used.
		It is not the meaning of the word, but the use of the word that is the problem
	From 7 we start talking about [language games].
	At 37-71, this theme is discussed again
